          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Wave makes adventure effortless. From high-performance <a href=\"/collections/sup-range\" title=\"SUP Range | Inflatable Paddle Boards\">paddleboards (SUPs)</a> <a href=\"/collections/kayak-and-canoe-range\" title=\"Kayak & Canoe Range | Inflatable Kayaks & Canoes\">kayaks and canoes</a> to <a href=\"/products/wave-3-in-1-robe\" title=\"3 in 1 Changing Robe | Unisex\">premium robes</a>, everything is built for the outdoors. Our paddleboards feature the world’s safest quick-release leash for maximum safety and control. Whether you're out solo or with family, Wave gear is made to perform. Easy setup guides and a responsive team mean you're ready to go, wherever the water takes you.<br/><br/>Need help? Our friendly team and easy setup guides have you covered. Float, soak, switch off, <strong>Wave’s got you.</strong></p>",
